Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.95,0:00:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呐 集 幫我把這個打開
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.83,0:00:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？你要去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.87,0:00:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之前說過的 社團的合宿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.59,0:00:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 哦 好像是說過
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.65,0:00:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.36,0:00:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.10,0:00:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要暫時離家幾天了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.26,0:00:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？要留下我一個人獨守空房？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.18,0:00:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這也是沒辦法的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.58,0:00:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會寂寞的 帶我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.06,0:00:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你好重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.06,0:00:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 祈醬
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.94,0:00:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,集要把我丟下不管了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.46,0:00:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了啦 快放手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.49,0:00:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目的地是大島嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.14,0:00:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.56,0:00:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.74,0:01:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那 就去見見父親吧
Comment: 0,0:02:44.00,0:02:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
